source.inline:
printf "\e[33m\e[1mAction is the foundational key to all success.
\e[0m~ Picasso"
set cpu to do shell script "ps axo %cpu | awk '{s+=$1}END{print s}'"return cpu & "%"

actionAppleScript.inline: activate application "Activity Monitor"tell application "System Events"	tell process "Activity Monitor"		tell radio button "CPU" of radio group 1 of group 2 of toolbar 1 of window 1 to perform action "AXPress"	end tellend tell

source.inline: set mem to do shell script "ps -A -o %mem | awk '{s+=$1}END{print s}'"return mem & "%"

actionAppleScript.inline: activate application "Activity Monitor"tell application "System Events"	tell process "Activity Monitor"		tell radio button "CPU" of radio group 1 of group 2 of toolbar 1 of window 1 to perform action "AXPress"	end tellend tell

source.inline: if application "Music" is running thentell application "Music"if player state is playing thenreturn (get artist of current track) & "  " & (get name of current track)elsereturn ""end ifend tellend ifreturn ""

actionAppleScript.inline: if application "Music" is running thentell application "Music"if player state is playing thennext trackend ifend tellend if

longActionAppleScript.inline: if application "Music" is running thentell application "Music"if player state is playing thenprev trackend ifend tellend if
